s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5820:"<p>Some users informed me, that the new settings panel introduced in v2.9 was broken when certain languages (French, Spanish, Italian&#8230;) were active. This is why I release v2.9.2 which fixes this bug and also adds a great new feature <img src='http://cdn.mapsmarker.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_wink.gif' alt=';-)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
<p>One personal request: as WordPress added a new review feature for plugins hosted on wordpress.org, I kindly invite you to leave your opinion about my plugin at <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/leaflet-maps-marker" target="_blank">http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/leaflet-maps-marker</a>.</p>
<p>Here´s what´s new in detail in v2.9.2:</p>
<p><strong>compatibility with 1st WordPress NFC plugin from pingeb.org </strong></p>
<p>I am really exited, that the first NFC plugin for WordPress from pingeb.org uses Leaflet Maps Marker. pingeb.org is a great new Austrian NFC project which aim was to build a virtual library for the city of Klagenfurt. In the meantime, the project team released the source code to make the use of this fantastic plugin available in every city world wide. Please <a href="http://www.mapsmarker.com/pingeb" target="_blank">follow this link</a> to read more about this great project.</p>
<p><strong>Translations updates</strong></p>
<p>Thanks to many motivated contributors, v2.9.2 comes with the following translation updates:</p>
<p>Updated translations</p>
<ul>
<li>Chinese translation thanks to John Shen, <a href="http://www.synyan.net" target="_blank">http://www.synyan.net</a></li>
<li>Dutch translation thanks to Patrick Ruers, <a href="http://www.stationskwartiersittard.nl" target="_blank">http://www.stationskwartiersittard.nl</a></li>
<li>French translation thanks to Vincèn Pujol, <a href="http://www.skivr.com" target="_blank">http://www.skivr.com</a> and Rodolphe Quiedeville, <a href="http://rodolphe.quiedeville.org/" target="_blank">http://rodolphe.quiedeville.org/</a></li>
<li>Ukrainian translation thanks to Andrexj, <a href="http://all3d.com.ua" target="_blank">http://all3d.com.ua</a></li>
<li>German translation</li>
</ul>
<p>If you want to contribute to translations, please visit <a href="http://translate.mapsmarker.com/projects/lmm" target="_blank">http://translate.mapsmarker.com/projects/lmm</a> for more information.</p>
<p><strong>Bugfix: new settings panel was broken when certain translations were loaded</strong></p>
<p>The problem with the new settings panel introduced in v2.9 occured if certain translations like French, Spanish or Italien were active. This is now fixed &amp; double checked for every available translation.</p>
<p><strong>Outlook &#8211; my plans for the next release<br />
</strong></p>
<p>I am currently working hard on preparing a pro version with even more features like adding markers from frontend, marker clustering, gpx support and more. More details about this version will follow soon.</p>
<p><strong>Full changelog </strong>(<a title="Releases / Changelog" href="http://www.mapsmarker.com/docs/changelog/">show previous changelogs</a>)<strong><br />
</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>NEW: compatibility with 1st WordPress NFC plugin from pingeb.org &#8211; <a href="http://www.mapsmarker.com/pingeb" target="_blank">read more</a></li>
<li>CHANGED: updated Chinese translation thanks to John Shen, <a href="http://www.synyan.net" target="_blank">http://www.synyan.net</a></li>
<li>CHANGED: updated Dutch translation thanks to Patrick Ruers, <a href="http://www.stationskwartiersittard.nl" target="_blank">http://www.stationskwartiersittard.nl</a></li>
<li>CHANGED: updated French translation thanks to Vincèn Pujol, <a href="http://www.skivr.com" target="_blank">http://www.skivr.com</a> and Rodolphe Quiedeville, <a href="http://rodolphe.quiedeville.org/" target="_blank">http://rodolphe.quiedeville.org/</a></li>
<li>CHANGED: updated Ukrainian translation thanks to Andrexj, <a href="http://all3d.com.ua" target="_blank">http://all3d.com.ua</a></li>
<li>CHANGED: updated German translation</li>
<li>FIXED: new settings panel was broken when certain translations were loaded</li>
</ul>
